# Uncomment and fill in the provider you want to use.
# Only ONE is needed.

# --- FREE OPTIONS ---

# Gemini (recommended — free, no credit card required)
# Get key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...

# Groq (free tier — very fast inference)
# Get key: https://console.groq.com/keys
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# Ollama (fully local — no key needed, just install from https://ollama.com)
# Run: ollama pull llama3.1:8b && ollama serve

# --- PAID OPTIONS ---

# Anthropic Claude
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# OpenAI
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
